<script type="text/javascript">
    window.easemobim = window.easemobim || {};
    easemobim.config = {
        hide: false,
        autoConnect: false
    };
    var index = 0;
    //抖动效果
    function imShakes() {
        var intShakes = 3;
        var intDistance = 40;
        var intDuration = 300
        var im = $("div.im-container");
        for (var x = 1; x <= intShakes; x++) {
            im.animate({ right: (40) }, (((intDuration / intShakes) / 4)))
                .animate({ right: 60 }, ((intDuration / intShakes) / 2))
                .animate({ right: 50 }, (((intDuration / intShakes) / 4)));
        }
    }
    //打开在线客服
    //function openEasemobimOnline() {
    //    $("#easemobimOnline").click();
    //}
    //var shakesTimer = setInterval(openEasemobimOnline, 30000);
    //$("div.im-container").on("click", function () {
    //    clearInterval(shakesTimer);
    //})
    $("#btnImSubmit").click(function () {
        var resultcheck = checkinput();
        if (resultcheck != "") {
            alert(resultcheck);
            return;
        }
        else {
            $.ajax({
                url: '/HomeSubPage/OnlineImScheduled',
                type: 'POST',
                data:
                {
                    ContractName: $("#ContractName").val(),
                    Category: $("#Category").val(),
                    Content: $("#Content").val(),
                    Phone: $("#Phone").val(),
                    Email: $("#Email").val(),
                    Startdate: $("#date-beginqq").val(),
                    Enddate: $("#date-endqq").val()
                },
                dataType: 'text',
                cache: true,
                success: function (res) {
                    var data = JSON.parse(res);
                    if (data.Success) {
                        alert("预约成功,本次在线洽谈预约在咨询专家受理后,将发送腾讯会议邀请码至您留的联系邮箱,请注意查收!");
                        layer.close(index);
                    }
                    else {
                        layer.alert(data.Message);
                    }
                }
            });
        }
    });
    $('#online-talk-x').on('click',
        function () {
            index = layer.open({
                type: 1,
                title: '在线洽谈',
                area: ['720px', '535px'],
                shade: 0,
                shadeClose: false, // 点击遮罩关闭,
                skin: 'layer-ext-moon',
                btnAlign: 'c',
                content: $('#edit-onlineTalkContent'),
                cancel: function () {
                    $('#edit-onlineTalkContent').hide();
                }
            });
        });
    function checkinput() {
        var result = "";
        if ($("#ContractName").val() == "") {
            result = result + "联系人必填 \n";
        }
        if ($("#Category").val() == "") {
            result = result + "咨询类型必填 \n";
        }
        if ($("#Phone").val() == "") {
            result = result + "联系手机必填 \n";
        }
        else {
            if (!(/^1[3456789]\d{9}$/.test($("#Phone").val()))) {
                result = result + "联系手机格式错误 \n";
            }
        }
        if ($("#Email").val() == "") {
            result = result + "联系邮箱必填 \n";
        }
        else {
            var regeee = /^([a-zA-Z0-9]+[_|\_|\.]?)*[a-zA-Z0-9]+@([a-zA-Z0-9]+[_|\_|\.]?)*[a-zA-Z0-9]+\.[a-zA-Z]{2,3}$/;
            if (!regeee.test($("#Email").val())) {
                result = result + "联系邮箱格式错误 \n";
            }
        }
        if ($("#date-beginqq").val() == "") {
            result = result + "建议开始时间必填 \n";
        }
        if ($("#date-endqq").val() == "") {
            result = result + "建议结束时间必填 \n";
        }
        return result;
    }
    function initLayDateqq() {
        laydate.render({
            elem: '#date-beginqq',
            format: 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss',
            type: 'datetime',
            //eventElem: '#fa-date-beginqq',
            trigger: 'click'
        })
        laydate.render({
            elem: '#date-endqq',
            format: 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss',
            type: 'datetime',
            // eventElem: '#fa-date-endqq',
            trigger: 'click'
        })
    }
    $(document).ready(function () {
        initLayDateqq();
    })
</script>
<script src="/Content/static/plugins/laydate/laydate.js"></script>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    function GetArticleListByCategory(categoryId) {
        $.ajax({
            url: '/HomeSubPage/ArticlesListHtml?CategoryId=' + categoryId,
            type: 'GET',
            data:
            {
                argCategoryId: categoryId
            },
            dataType: 'html',
            cache: true,
            success: function (data) {
                ///alert(data);
                if (data == "") {
                    $("#divArtilceList").html("");
                }
                $("#divArtilceList").html(data);
            }
        });
    }
    function LinkToArticle(articleId) {
        window.location.href = '/HomeSubPage/ArticlesDetails' + "?argArticleId=" + articleId;
    }
    $(function () {
        //智能归类/申报要素查询
        $("#searchOne").click(function () {
            var search = $("#declarationEl").val();
            if (search == "") {
                window.location.href = 'http://kw.hscode.net/';
            }
            else {
                if (parseInt(search)) {
                    window.location.href = 'http://kw.hscode.net/' + 'AI/AIHscode?kw=' + search;
                }
                else {
                    window.location.href = 'http://kw.hscode.net/' + 'AI/AIItems?kw=' + search;
                }
            }
        });
        //运单跟踪
        $("#searchTwo").click(function () {
            var search = $("#orderNo").val();
            window.location.href = "http://new.wherexpress.com/index.php?r=track%2Findex&assbillno=" + search;
            window.location.href = "#";
        });
        //美国关税查询
        $("#searchThird").click(function () {
            var search = $("#taxation").val();
            if (search == "") {
                window.location.href = 'http://kw.us.hscode.net/';
            }
            else {
                window.location.href = 'http://kw.us.hscode.net/' + 'HTS/AIHtsCodeList?htskw=' + search;
            }
        });
        //文章--口岸物流动态

            GetArticleListByCategory("9F763120-D41E-4467-86C8-4C992C9F2557");
        });
        //文章--海关公告

        });
